    <introduction>
      <para>Error B1X0001: A help compiler path must be specified</para>
    </introduction>

    <section>
      <title>Cause</title>
      <content>
        <para>This error occurs if the <codeInline>HelpCompilerFolder</codeInline>
property on the <codeInline>Build1xHelpFile</codeInline> build task has not
been set or is set to an empty string.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

    <section>
      <title>Solution</title>
      <content>
        <para>Specify a valid path for the <codeInline>HelpCompilerFolder</codeInline>
property on the <codeInline>Build1xHelpFile</codeInline> build task in the
project file.</para>
      </content>
    </section>

